remixlab.bias.branch

Class GenericEventGrabberTuple<E extends Enum<E>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • remixlab.bias.core.EventGrabberTuple
      • remixlab.bias.branch.GenericEventGrabberTuple<E>

  • public class GenericEventGrabberTuple<E extends Enum<E>>
extends EventGrabberTuple
    A [BogusEvent,GenericGrabber, Action] tuple. An enqueued tuple fires a Grabber.performInteraction(BogusEvent) call from the event in the tuple. For details refer to the GenericGrabber documentation.

    Tuples are typically enqueued by an agent (through their branches, see Agent.handle(BogusEvent)), but may be enqueued manually, see InputHandler.enqueueEventTuple(EventGrabberTuple).
